uscrito (28x28 pixels) em um dos 10 d\u00edgitos (0-9).", "layout": "example_highlight", "reason": "sentence_normalization", "mutated": false, "function": "ensureSentenceEnd", "event_type": "fit_adjustment", "chars_after": 107, "chars_before": 107, "reduction_pct": 0}, {"after": "Solu\u00e7\u00e3o: A camada de entrada teria 784 neur\u00f4nios, uma camada oculta com 128 neur\u00f4nios, e a de sa\u00edda com 10 neur\u00f4nios e fun\u00e7\u00e3o Softmax.", "field": "item[1]", "slide": 12, "stage": "2.5", "before": "Solu\u00e7\u00e3o: A camada de entrada teria 784 neur\u00f4nios, uma camada oculta com 128 neur\u00f4nios, e a de sa\u00edda com 10 neur\u00f4nios e fun\u00e7\u00e3o Softmax.", "layout": "example_highlight", "reason": "sentence_normalization", "mutated": false, "function": "ensureSentenceEnd", "event_type": "fit_adjustment", "chars_after": 134, "chars_before": 134, "reduction_pct": 0}, {"after": "Resultado: A rede indica a probabilidade de a imagem ser cada d\u00edgito, resultando na classifica\u00e7\u00e3o final.", "field": "item[2]", "slide": 12, "stage": "2.5", "before": "Resultado: A rede indica a probabilidade de a imagem ser cada d\u00edgito, resultando na classifica\u00e7\u00e3o final.", "layout": "example_highlight", "reason": "sentence_normalization", "mutated": false, "function": "ensureSentenceEnd", "event_type": "fit_adjustment", "chars_after": 104, "chars_before": 104, "reduction_pct": 0}, {"after": "Como a inspira\u00e7\u00e3o biol\u00f3gica contribui para a capacidade das Redes Neurais de resolver problemas complexos?", "field": "item[0]", "slide": 13, "stage": "2.5", "before": "Como a inspira\u00e7\u00e3o biol\u00f3gica contribui para a capacidade das Redes Neurais de resolver problemas complexos?", "layout": "reflection_callout", "reason": "sentence_normalization", "mutated": false, "function": "ensureSentenceEnd", "event_type": "fit_adjustment", "chars_after": 106, "chars_before": 106, "reduction_pct": 0}, {"after": "De que forma a fun\u00e